    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this beauty from day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. No scratches, no smells, just pure perfection. You really have to see it to believe how gorgeous it is. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see this go to a great home!",
