    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This specimen delivers a linear power band via six individual throttle bodies and a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The mechanical provenance is documented and complete: the rod bearings and Vanos solenoids have been proactively replaced, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. The chassis retains its factory-correct geometry with no bushing deflection, while the M-Variable differential provides optimal lock-up under load. Finished in its original paint with zero oxidation and an interior devoid of bolster wear, this is a turn-key, collector-grade example for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
