    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade specimen that defies its age. This vehicle has been fastidiously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and presents in showroom condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like luster with zero rock chips or swirl marks, further protected by a multi-layer ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains a time capsule; the leather bolsters are firm and free of creases, the dashboard is devoid of any UV exposure, and it retains that distinct factory-new scent. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is superlative, backed by a comprehensive, chronological binder of every service performed since its delivery. It sits on fresh, premium tires and has recently undergone a preventative major fluid service. This is a rare opportunity to own a flawless, museum-quality example for the most discerning collector.",
