    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 in museum-quality condition. This S54-powered icon features a factory-spec 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six with crisp individual throttle body response and a seamless double VANOS system. Mechanically overhauled with preventative rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a perfectly calibrated limited-slip differential. Finished in its original Carbon Black Metallic with zero paint correction required, this example retains its factory-fresh suspension kinematics and OEM forged Style 67 wheels. A true turnkey collector piece for the discerning purist.",
